{"tid":1968657,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解USB係而家係最成功嘅port?","createTime":"2020-04-11T21:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T12:44:21.000Z","uid":104378,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"deddc3f126e28a6ce27389aa0326d78c636f2c4f","tid":1968657,"uid":104378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:41:10.000Z","msg":"因為佢多人用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起USB同FireWire同出現之前<br />\n有scsi parallel port serial port ps/2...<br />\n數都數唔晒<br />\n唔同嘅device要插唔同port<br />\n跟本傾唔到計<br />\n9x年後期有左USB/FireWire開始革命<br />\n大家先可以開始一條線搞掂啲周邊設備<br />\n<br />\nUSB係好多間大廠整出嚟<br />\nFireWire係Apple整出嚟<br />\n<br />\nUSB好慢98年修正完先得12Mbps(half-duplex)<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">-&gt;upload+download=12Mbps</span><br />\nFireWire 95年一出就有400Mbps(full-duplex)<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">-&gt;upload/download各自有400Mbps</span><br />\n<br />\nUSB一個頭連一個device再多就用hub<br />\nFireWire可以用Daisy chain連最多63個devices<br />\n<br />\nUSB會佔用cpu又慢<br />\nFireWire 佔用好少又快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins><strong><em>FireWire失敗嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Apple鐘意玩<span style=\"color: red;\">高竇</span><br />\n個<span style=\"color: red;\">Standard又高</span><br />\n收license錢勁貴（初頭逐個收1-2usd）<br />\n後尾嘅FireWire 800又同之前個接口唔同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span>埋自己啲product<br />\n跟本得佢自己同High end product<span style=\"color: red;\">圍爐</span><br />\nEx iPod、<br />\nSony HDV(仲要為左避license改左名iLink<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><em><ins>USB成功嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大廠<span style=\"color: red;\">合作</span>整出嚟<br />\n好平嘅license錢甚至免費<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">超低門檻個個都好樂意做</span><br />\n最初嘅USB1.1至USB3.0都係用type A頭<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單直接</span>兼容到<br />\n個個都用全部人都識<br />\n所以USB係<span style=\"color: red;\">無處不在</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">理所當然</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">雖然啲大廠都係敵人<br />\n但過程同效能好似唔係最緊要<br />\n好似有共識點到先係關鍵</span><br />\n<br />\n同類型嘅例子仲有好多<br />\n老一輩應該知Sony betamax vs VHS?<br />\n新嘅有Sony memory stick vs SD Card?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係返屋企用FireWire幫我部iPod 1st gen入歌<br />\n幾秒就過完一隻碟<br />\n仲要support最新嘅mac os catalina<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSor我係Apple狗"},{"pid":"dc8e6933d9b14091bd79cffd46611a17cedce67a","tid":1968657,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:45:41.000Z","msg":"cheap"},{"pid":"e53ddc7862ed4780cfc0ff3c93b616ab3e5a8591","tid":1968657,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:49:25.000Z","msg":"原來apple咁耐以前已經走high end"},{"pid":"dee6c0244fe39341eac2fc57dba36d322f944b9d","tid":1968657,"uid":104378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e53ddc7862ed4780cfc0ff3c93b616ab3e5a8591","tid":1968657,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:49:25.000Z","msg":"原來apple咁耐以前已經走high end"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:54:10.000Z","msg":"太pro同requirement太高玩死自己"},{"pid":"833cd9642c425c3e60298ce59344e9a9cd708392","tid":1968657,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:56:16.000Z","msg":"反而想知點解宜家啲電腦機箱新出個啲都仲夠膽死俾usb 2.0 你，仲可以一個type c 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874ba8e8093b295234e84a591c514bbbd2207017","tid":1968657,"uid":227573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833cd9642c425c3e60298ce59344e9a9cd708392","tid":1968657,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"